      "title": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Langkawi Adventure & Xtreme Park"
          }
        ]
      },
      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "If you’re looking for a fun day out among nature, then this attraction is for you! Set out on a journey to Langkawi and into the Kilim Geoforest Park, a UNESCO listed heritage geo site, where the Langkawi Adventure & Xtreme Park is located. Here, experience the thrill of pedaling on a bike over a suspended cable, ziplining, paintball, and go-karting, among others, while surrounded by native flora. Bring your friends along and take turns trying out exciting activities that will surely make you want to go again.You can also choose to do activities that could help you unwind, such as going on a horseback ride or visiting the unique 3D Art Museum, where you’re free to goof around. Following the park’s trails and admiring the landscape is always an option as well. There’s something for everyone at the Langkawi Adventure & Xtreme Park!"
          }
        ]
      },
      "rating": {
        "average_value": 4.3,
        "rating_count": 100
      },
      "product_features": [
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "ATV Jungle Ride: An adventurous ride through the jungle on an All-Terrain Vehicle (ATV)."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Jungle Horse Riding: Experience horse riding in the lush greenery of the jungle."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Flying Fox: Soar through the air on a zip-line, also known as the Flying Fox."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Indoor Go-Kart: Enjoy the thrill of racing in a safe and controlled indoor environment."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Langkawi Sky Bike: The latest addition to the park, the Sky Bike offers a unique and thrilling way to explore the park from above."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Prepare to unleash your inner explorer as you choose from over 12 exciting activities.  Take a thrilling ride on an ATV through a lush jungle landscape, weaving through muddy tracks and feeling the wind in your hair.  For a different perspective, soar through the treetops on the Sky Bike, a high-altitude cycling adventure that offers breathtaking panoramic views of the rainforest.  If you prefer terra firma, test your driving skills on the Go-Kart track, navigating tight corners and experiencing the exhilaration of a high-speed race.The park caters to more than just speed demons.  Challenge your aim with archery or test your courage on the Flying Fox zipline, soaring across a scenic valley.  For a family-friendly activity, explore the various horse riding options, suitable for both beginners and experienced riders.  Langkawi Adventure &amp; Xtreme Park even features a 3D and 7D cinema experience, transporting you to fantastical worlds for a touch of virtual reality fun."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Accessibility: The park's overall layout with uneven terrain and limited ramps might pose challenges for visitors with wheelchairs or mobility impairments."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Restriction: Some activities, like ATV rides or the Sky Bike, have minimum age and height restrictions."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Restriction:  Large bags, backpacks, and loose items are not recommended on rides or during activities."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
